OL,7,FVideo report by ITV News reporter
OL,8,FBarnaby Papadopulos
OL,10,FThe family of a man who died in a
OL,11,Fcrash just three minutes away from
OL,12,Fhome are calling for improvements to
OL,13,Fbe made to a major road in the south of
OL,15,FTony Sheil, 51, died on 24 November
OL,16,F2023 on the A75 between Newton Stewart
OL,17,Fand Stranraer when his van collided
OL,18,Fwith a lorry on his way home from work.
OL,20,FA police investigation into the
OL,21,Fincident is ongoing.
