OL,7,FThe A75 stretches 95 miles from As
OL,8,Fwell as being used by commuters, it is
OL,9,Fa major freight route, with hundreds
OL,10,Fof lorries using it everyday to access
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland bound ferries from
OL,12,Fthe port at Cairnryan.
OL,14,FTony's partner of 36 years, Michaela
OL,15,FYates, said she first knew something
OL,16,Fwas wrong when his phone tracker
OL,17,Fstopped suddenly as he was driving
OL,18,Fhome.
