OL,7,F"I don't know how long it was. It felt
OL,8,Flike forever," she said. "Then two
OL,9,Fpolice officers came and they said
OL,10,Fthey think it was Tony."
OL,12,FMr Sheil's daughter Samantha-Jane
OL,13,Flearnt to drive 12 months ago but has
OL,14,Fnot felt able to get behind the wheel
OL,15,Fsince the crash.
OL,17,F"I was working at the same place dad
OL,18,Fwas working at and I left. If I didn't
OL,19,Fleave, I would have been behind him or
OL,20,Fwith him," she explained. "That's
OL,21,Freally scary to think about."
