OL,7,FShe has now launched a petition
OL,8,Fcalling for changes to the road, which
OL,9,Fhas been signed by over 700 people.
OL,11,F"I want improvements on the road," she
OL,12,Fsaid. "The potholes are just mad. I do
OL,13,Fwant speed cameras and I did want it
OL,14,Fduelled."
