OL,7,FIain Dick, of group Dual the A75,
OL,8,Fsaid: "In the last two years, we've
OL,9,Fseen HGVs go over at the halfway
OL,10,Fhouse. We've seen a horrendous HGV
OL,11,Faccident in Crocketford, we've seen a
OL,12,Fdeath near Sheraton in November and
OL,13,Fwe've seen another death on the Annan
OL,14,Fbypass recently.
OL,16,F"What more evidence do you need to
OL,17,Fhave to say that this road is not
OL,18,Fsafe?"
